Zambia’s Sata Names Guy Scott as Vice President, Times Says

-- B y   N a s r e e n   S e r i a
-- 
2011-09-29T11:52:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-29/zambia-s-sata-names-guy-scott-as-vice-president-times-says.html
Zambian President  Michael Sata 
appointed Guy Scott, deputy of Sata’s Patriotic Front, as vice
president of the country, the Lusaka Times reported today.  The Cabinet was reduced to 19 ministries from 22, the
newspaper said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nasreen Seria at 
 nseria@bloomberg.net  